    "asOf": "2006-04-06",
    "date": "2006-05-05T20:12:28Z",
    "text": "Taxpayer Information Protection and Privacy Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to prohibit tax return preparers from: (1) soliciting taxpayers for consent to the disclosure or use of their tax return information for any purpose; and (2) disclosing tax return information to tax preparers located outside the United States without taxpayer consent."
